nethack367: nethack367 (Rogue-like game)
nethack367:
nethack367: Nethack is a single-player dungeon exploration game. The emphasis is
nethack367: on discovering the detail of the dungeon. Each game presents a
nethack367: different landscape - the random number generator provides an
nethack367: essentially unlimited number of variations of the dungeon and its
nethack367: denizens to be discovered by the player in one of a number of
nethack367: characters: you can pick your race, your role, and your gender.
